[commands]

[name]
check_ide_smart

[info]
This plugin checks a local hard drive with the (Linux specific) SMART interface <a href="http://smartlinux.sourceforge.net/smart/index.php" target="_blank">http://smartlinux.sourceforge.net/smart/index.php</a>.

[why]
To get control over the local hard drives on your server.

[how]
By checking the local hard drive with ioctl.

[platforms]
Linux host with the SMART interface installed.

[categories]
Hardware
